title: Indiana Jones and the Sargasso Pirates 1-4 of 4
description: Written by Karl Kesel. Art by Karl Kesel, Paul Guinan and Eduardo Barreto. Cover by Alex Ross. Indiana Jones sails the high seas in search of a lost Viking ship! Having signed on with a band of pirates, Indy has placed his life in the hands of his old nemesis, Captain Lawton, who blames Indy for the loss of his leg to a shark years earlier. But sharks are the least of anyone's worries when the vessel becomes entangled in the mythical graveyard of ships -- the Sargasso Sea!
